{"tid":1957514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"官網宣傳四缺一！粉絲不滿Jisoo遭忽略要求品牌道歉","createTime":"2020-04-04T03:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T11:13:36.000Z","uid":1086,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab33346cae2114c4f5820f6567dae1edd3117c8","tid":1957514,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1yyHNCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1yyHNCO.jpg&h=d306a779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁大細超？<br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣女國BLACKPINK自出道後就有不少成員遭到差別待遇的傳聞，粉絲都紛紛為自家<br />\n偶像抱不平。然而近日卻再有不愉快事件發生，以致Jisoo的粉絲更強烈要求品牌方面道<br />\n歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L0M2Xz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FL0M2Xz7.jpg&h=68bef52b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本的組合宣傳圖（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n作為全球人氣女團BLACKPINK自然是代言界的寵兒，無論是組合還是個人都代言了不少大<br />\n牌子。2018年起BLACKPINK便成為國際知名運動品牌adidas的代言人之一，成員日常也經<br />\n常穿著品牌產品，又在社交網站上宣傳，可以說是非常盡責。不過近日有粉絲就發現品牌<br />\n官網上有關BLACKPINK的宣傳圖片竟然4缺1！明明是4人的合照卻被裁剪成只有Lisa、<br />\nJennie和ROS&Eacute;，Jisoo完全不見蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gE7LzfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgE7LzfF.png&h=332b9271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網上4缺1（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KEw16gW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKEw16gW.png&h=f2831158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網上4缺1（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n事件爆出後迅即引起大批粉絲的不滿，同時也發現更多差別待遇的事實，例如店鋪內和網<br />\n站的單人宣傳海報唯獨缺了Jisoo、4人海報Jisoo莫名其妙被剪開等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tes8g99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ftes8g99.png&h=edd36a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店內單人海報也是4缺1（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/To40NLY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTo40NLY.png&h=3d47c5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網單人宣傳圖4缺1（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ztDwRbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FztDwRbD.png&h=235060e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4人海報Jisoo莫名奇妙被剪開（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n對比Jisoo經常透過個人IG宣傳品牌，如此差別待遇令粉絲十分生氣又替她非常不值，於<br />\n是在Twitter上刷起「#AdidasApologizeToJisoo」的話題，要求品牌道歉之餘也希望可以<br />\n公平對待每一位BLACKPINK成員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hFCPkI2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhFCPkI2.png&h=e6eb9e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJisoo經常在IG為品牌宣傳，非常稱職（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"6a45c0aea8f5baa5ea5c69915683eae0b36eb46d","tid":1957514,"uid":4574,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"最靚嗰嗰 反而無圖？<br />\nMarketing 食得屎"},{"pid":"a82ec003057f8e5325fc3af761ebdfa903483497","tid":1957514,"uid":1086,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"Kpop史上第一隊冇團fan既女團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997f59115f8c2a7475520beccca962465adbc762","tid":1957514,"uid":84673,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"Jisoo 最正"},{"pid":"e7170d2aef24215f96f4c64e69fa4795e8f2a8ea","tid":1957514,"uid":170044,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:56:13.000Z","msg":"中左流感要隔離?"},{"pid":"947af38d83a0229a759585a7ea8442aed85bb5d5","tid":1957514,"uid":3204,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a45c0aea8f5baa5ea5c69915683eae0b36eb46d","tid":1957514,"uid":4574,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"最靚嗰嗰 反而無圖？<br />\nMarketing 食得屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"事實係最唔紅果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3d6bf682f795013b421d956b890a1ee0bddc09","tid":1957514,"uid":136880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,